        <description>&lt;p&gt;React library prior to 0.0.7 (versions 0.0.6 and earlier) have outdated proof-of-work implementation and may take significantly longer time to compute now. Update to 0.0.7+ to resolve this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
        <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;React library prior to 0.0.7 (versions 0.0.6 and earlier) have outdated proof-of-work implementation and may take significantly longer time to compute now. Update to 0.0.7+ to resolve this.&lt;/p&gt;
